- Even with your research skill maxed out, you will get many failures when you try to make a spell as soon as you are able, eg researching a lvl24 spell at lvl24<br>
- Best to find your components and ask a senior mage to Combine for you<br>
- Increase your research skills so that you can return the favour some day<br>
- Concordance of Research is a waste of time, too much effort for too little return<br>
- Components can sometimes be found on NPC traders, especially in areas like Shadow Haven, Freeport, Firiona Vie, The Overthere.  Be patient keep looking, especially a few hours after a patch<br>
- Ask senior guild members to keep a lookout for components<br>
- ALL 34 - 44 pet spells can be found in Katta.  Repeat... ALL<br>
